# Project Overview — Mitesh Sir's Group Tuitions

A full-stack **tuition management web application** for ISC Accountancy & Commerce coaching. It uses a **static HTML/CSS/JS frontend** connected to a **Google Apps Script + Google Sheets backend**.

---

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Frontend
        A[index.html] --> B[login.html]
        B --> C[teacher_dashboard.html]
        B --> D[student_dashboard.html]
        A --> E[results.html]
        A --> F[testimonials.html]
    end
    subgraph Shared JS
        G[js/config.js] --> H[js/app.js]
    end
    subgraph Backend
        I["Google Apps Script (Code.gs)"]
        J[Google Sheets DB]
        K[Google Drive Storage]
    end
    H -- "fetch API" --> I
    I --> J
    I --> K
```

