## Design System

- **Font**: Outfit (headings) + Inter (body), via Google Fonts
- **Color palette**: Warm cream base (`#EADDCA`), steel-blue primary (`#7393B3`), sage-green secondary (`#8A9A5B`)
- **UI style**: Glassmorphism panels with `backdrop-filter: blur(16px)`, soft shadows, warm tones
- **Animations**: `fadeUp` keyframe, hover lifts (`translateY(-5px)`)

---

## Key Features

### Public Pages
- **Landing** ([index.html](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/index.html)) — Hero section, stats (10+ years, 100% passing, 5k+ students, 50+ toppers)
- **Results** ([results.html](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/results.html)) — Filterable table of student results (by subject, year, name search)
- **Testimonials** ([testimonials.html](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/testimonials.html)) — Student success stories loaded from Google Sheets

### Authentication ([login.html](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/login.html))
- Role toggle (Student / Teacher) with URL param support (`?role=teacher`)
- Credentials validated against Google Sheets (Students/Teachers tabs)
- `localStorage`-based session via `auth` module in [app.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/js/app.js)

### Teacher Dashboard ([teacher_dashboard.html](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/teacher_dashboard.html)) — 5 Tabs
1. **Upload Material** — File upload to Google Drive with title, grade, subjects (Accounts/Commerce)
2. **Post Announcement** — Announcements targeted by grade
3. **Schedule Test** — Create tests with subject, grade, max marks
4. **Manage Marks** — Select test → enter marks per student
5. **Student List** — View all students + "Add Student" form with auto-generated IDs (`STU-YYYY-NNN`)

### Student Dashboard ([student_dashboard.html](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/student_dashboard.html))
- **Study Materials** — Filterable by subject, searchable by title
- **Announcements** — Latest notices
- **Tests & Marks** — Table of test results

---

## Backend (Google Apps Script)

All data lives in a **single Google Sheets** spreadsheet with these tabs:

| Sheet Tab | Columns |
|---|---|
| Teachers | Username, Password, Name, Role |
| Students | Student ID, Name, Role, Username, Password, Grade, Subjects |
| Files | File ID, Title, Description, Subject, Class, Upload Date, File URL |
| Results | Student Name, Class, Subject, Score, Rank, File Link |
| Testimonials | ID, Student Name, Year, Subject, Testimonial Text, Photo URL |
| Announcements | Date, Title, Message, Class |
| Tests | Test ID, Date, Title, Subject, Class, Max Marks |
| Marks | Test ID, Student Username, Marks |

**API Endpoints** (via [doGet](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/backend/Code.gs#34-65) / [doPost](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Downloads/Software/AG%20Project%202/backend/Code.gs#8-33)):
- `GET`: getResults, getTestimonials, getFiles, getAnnouncements, getTests, getMarks, getStudents
- `POST`: login, uploadFile, addAnnouncement, scheduleTest, enterMarks, addStudent

File uploads go to a configured **Google Drive folder** and are linked in the spreadsheet.

---

## Skills & Workflows

The `.agent/` directory contains 6 custom skills: `brainstorming-ideas`, `committing-changes`, `creating-skills`, `creating-walkthroughs`, `planning-projects`, and `pushing-code`.
